rding to realistic values. We have achieved this through direct access to historical archives, a network of military experts and our advanced proprietary game engine that goes in depth like never before. Armor on tanks and aircraft, as well as their internal components, \nare modeled down to the millimeter. \n \nHIGHLY DETAILED DAMAGE MODELS \nOur damage models go into extreme detail with each component being destroyable in vehicles including crew, weapon storage, gas tanks and more! You don’t just shoot a hitbox? NO! With every shot fired, multiple calculations take place that determine the round impact consequences. Some of these include; angle of obliquity, speed of round at impact, thickness of the armor, internal spall, armor penetration, parts of tank damaged, etc. \n \nFAIR GAME PLAY FOR ALL \nJust like in real life, the outcome of each engagement will be determined by strategy, tactics, teamwork, and your weapon handling skills! In WWII Online there are no special power ups or item buys giving someone a special advantage against other players. Every rifle is just as lethal whether you are a premium subscriber or a free \nplayer.","popularity":1.666666666666667,"tags":[1073741825],"developers":[13557],"publishers":[146],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[1],"game_modes":[5],"keywords":[19],"themes":[1,22,38,39],"genres":[5,24],"first_release_date":1009756800000,"platforms":[6,14],"release_dates":[{"category":2,"platform":14,"date":1041292800000,"human":"2002","y":2002,"m":12},{"category":2,"platform":6,"date":1009756800000,"human":"2001","y":2001,"m":12}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"World War II Online: Battleground Europe"},{"name":"Battleground Europe"},{"name":"WWII Online: Battleground Europe"},{"name":"WWII Online","comment":"Acronym"}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/uhoizruh9hcfq4bjgmuw.jpg","cloudinary_id":"uhoizruh9hcfq4bjgmuw","width":1280,"height":800},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/nwqsrsn