u from season to season, with features including a new calendar view of the fixtures, new training to guide your players’ development, season stats for all the players in the league, and leaderboards for all stats categories. \n \nThe extensive team editing functions in the game allow you to edit the names of the County team players, and to edit all details of the Club teams; including the team name, uniform style and colours, and the names, appearance, and details of each of the players. \n \nThe game also includes support for the Cameo EyeToy and Digimask that allows a player to put his/her head into the game on top of one of the players. Four-player multiplayer is supported using the PS2 multitap. \n \nThe game comes with the Official GAA Hurling / Football skills DVD. This DVD features routines which can be practiced to help master the key skills of the game.","collection":4887,"popularity":1.666666666666667,"games":[44242,54662,18623,22470,29173,22425,26145,55590,55689,23867],"tags":[268435469,268435470,536872060,536872078,536872673,536873350,536875234,536878092,1073741826],"developers":[13918],"publishers":[334],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[2],"game_modes":[1,2],"keywords":[1148,1166,1761,2438,4322,7180],"genres":[13,14],"first_release_date":1194566400000,"platforms":[8],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":8,"date":1194566400000,"region":1,"human":"2007-Nov-09","y":2007,"m":11}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/wrdzjjhtt2tvcydcifbr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"wrdzjjhtt2tvcydcifbr","width":372,"height":281}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/lwhymsdrtyvx7bfcdvtd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"lwhymsdrtyvx7bfcdvtd","width":800,"height":1130},"pegi":{"rating":1}},{"id":73466,"name":"Crystalix","slug":"crystalix","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/crystalix","created_at":1507203363981,"updated_at":1515664044442,"popularity":1.0,"games":[55036,29173,55590,23345,19376,11362,9760,33603,36962,55888],"tags":[2684